ham]] || [[Peter Gunn (actor)|Peter Gunn]] || 2010\u20132013, 2015\u2013\n|-\n| [[Izzy Armstrong]] || [[Cherylee Houston]] || 2010\u2013\n|-\n| [[Faye Windass]] || [[Ellie Leach]] || 2011\u2013\n|-\n| [[Beth Tinker]] || [[Lisa George]] || 2011\u2013\n|-\n| [[Craig Tinker]] || Colson Smith || 2011\u2013\n|-\n| [[Tim Metcalfe (Coronation Street)|Tim Metcalfe]] || [[Joe Duttine]] || 2013\u2013\n|-\n| [[Alya Nazir]] || [[Sair Khan]] || 2014\u2013\n|-\n| [[Yasmeen Nazir]] || [[Shelley King]] || 2014\u2013\n|-\n| [[Gemma Winter]] || Dolly-Rose Campbell || 2014\u2013\n|-\n| [[Billy Mayhew]] || [[Daniel Brocklebank]] || 2014\u2013\n|-\n| [[Cathy Matthews]] || [[Melanie Hill]] || 2015\u2013\n|-\n| [[Alex Warner (Coronation Street)|Alex Warner]] || Liam Bairstow || 2015\u2013\n|-\n| [[Johnny Connor (Coronation Street)|Johnny Connor]] || [[Richard Hawley (actor)|Richard Hawley]] || 2015\u2013\n|-\n| [[Seb Franklin]] || Harry Visinoni || 2016\u2013\n|-\n| [[Shona Ramsey]] || [[Julia Goulding]] || 2016\u2013\n|-\n| [[List of Coronation Street characters (2017)#Moira Pollock|Moira Pollock]] || [[Louiza Patikas]] || 2017\u2013\n|-\n| [[Abi Franklin]] || [[Sally Carman]] || 2017\u2013\n|-\n| [[Imran Habeeb]] || Charlie de Melo || 2017\u2013\n|-\n| [[Geoff Metcalfe]] || [[Ian Bartholomew]] || 2018\u2013\n|-\n| [[Emma Brooker]] || Alexandra Mardell || 2018\u2013\n|-\n| [[Paul Foreman (Coronation Street)|Paul Foreman]] || [[Peter Ash]] || 2018\u2013\n|-\n| [[Paula Martin]] || [[Stirling Gallacher]] || 2018\u2013\n|-\n| [[Evelyn Plummer]] || [[Maureen Lipman]] || 2018\u2013\n|-\n| [[Alina Pop]] || Ruxandra Porojnicu || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[James Bailey (Coronation Street)|James Bailey]] || Nathan Graham || 2019\u2013 \n|-\n| [[Edison Bailey|Ed Bailey]] || Trevor Michael Georges || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[Michael Bailey (Coronation Street)|Michael Bailey]] || Ryan Russell || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[Aggie Bailey]] || [[Lorna Laidlaw]] || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[List of Coronation Street characters (2019)#Ray Crosby|Ray Crosby]] || [[Mark Frost (actor) | Mark Frost]] || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[Bernie Winter]] || [[Jane Hazlegrove]] || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[List of Coronation Street characters (2019)#Nina Lucas|Nina Lucas]] || Mollie Gallagher || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[Arthur Medwin]] || [[Paul Copley]] || 2020\u2013\n|}\n\n=== Recurring and guest characters ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:200px;\" | Character\n! style=\"width:200px;\" | Current actor\n! style=\"width:360px;\" | Character duration\n|-\n| [[Liam Connor Jr.]] || Charlie Wrenshall || 2009\u2013\n|-\n| [[Max Turner (Coronation Street)|Max Turner]] || Harry McDermott || 2010\u2013\n|-\n| [[Jack Webster (Coronation Street)|Jack Webster]] || Kyran Bowes || 2010\u2013\n|-\n| [[Hope Stape]] || Isabella Flanagan || 2010\u2013\n|-\n| [[Joseph Brown (Coronation Street)|Joseph Brown]] || William Flanagan || 2011\u20132015, 2017\u2013\n|-\n| [[Ruby Dobbs]] || Macy Alabi || 2012\u2013\n|-\n| [[Jake Windass]] || Bobby Bradshaw || 2013\u2013\n|-\n| [[Lily Platt]] || Brooke Malonie || 2013\u2013\n|-\n| [[Dr. Gaddas]] || Christine Mackie || 2014\u2013\n|-\t\n| [[Harry Platt (Coronation Street)|Harry Platt]] || Freddie and Isaac Rhodes || 2016\u2013\n|-\n| [[Oliver Battersby]] || Emmanuel and Jeremiah Cheetham || 2017\u2013\n|-\n| [[Summer Spellman]] || Matilda Freeman || 2017\u2013\n|-\n| [[Bertie Osbourne]] || Elias and Rufus Morgan-Smith and<br /> Ellis Blain || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[List of Coronation Street characters (2019)#Sharon Geary|Sharon Geary]] || Naomi Cooper-Davis || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| Corey Brent || Maximus Evans || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| [[List of Coronation Street characters (2019)#Kelly Neelan|Kelly Neelan]] || Millie Gibson || 2019\u2013\n|-\n| Pastal-Blue Ollerenshaw || Hannah Waring || 2019\u2013\n|- \n| [[List of Coronation Street characters (2019)#Aled, Carys, Llio and Bryn Winter-Brown|Aled Winter-Brown]] || rowspan=\"4\" | Charlotte and James Holt,<br /> and Arthur, Lily and Lucy T